The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves training separate classifiers for intensity and geometry information, which suggests the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of an ensemble of patches also suggests the possibility of multi-modal approaches (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves comparing results with other methods, which suggests the use of information retrieval techniques (cs.IR).
